@startuml annashres_CustomerBot

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<UI>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<Logic>> LightGreen
  BackgroundColor<<Data>> LightYellow
  BackgroundColor<<Integration>> LightPink
}

[Bot Framework Channels] as Channels <<UI>>
[Adaptive Cards] as Cards <<UI>>
[Bot Core Logic] as BotLogic <<Logic>>
[Display Manager] as Display <<Logic>>
[Authentication] as Auth <<Logic>>
[Fuzzy Matching] as Fuzzy <<Logic>>
[Azure SQL Database] as DB <<Data>>
[Email Parser] as EmailParser <<Integration>>
[Power BI Dashboard] as PowerBI <<Integration>>

Channels --> BotLogic : User input
BotLogic --> Cards : Generate UI
BotLogic --> Display : Format output
BotLogic --> Auth : Verify user
BotLogic --> Fuzzy : Match company names
BotLogic --> DB : Store/Retrieve data
BotLogic --> EmailParser : Parse email chains
BotLogic --> PowerBI : Provide data

DB --> PowerBI : Data for visualization

@enduml